statements: SELECT id, age, gender, race, income, education_level, program_suggestions FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY income DESC
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE race='Asian' AND income > 50000
SELECT id, gender, education_level FROM demographic_data WHERE gender='Female' ORDER BY id ASC
SELECT id, age, education_level FROM demographic_data WHERE age < 40 AND income < 40000
SELECT id, race, program_suggestions FROM demographic_data WHERE program_suggestions IS NOT NULL
SELECT id, age, gender FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY gender ASC
SELECT gender, race, income FROM demographic_data WHERE income < 50000 ORDER BY income DESC
SELECT id, age, race, education_level FROM demographic_data WHERE education_level LIKE '%Bachelor%' AND race = 'Asian'
SELECT id, gender, income FROM demographic_data WHERE gender = 'Male' AND income BETWEEN 50000 AND 75000 ORDER BY id DESC
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE race = 'Black' OR race = 'White' AND program_suggestions IS NOT NULL
SELECT age, gender FROM demographic_data;
SELECT program_name, program_type FROM educational_programs;
SELECT ethnicity, income FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 30;
SELECT program_name, program_duration FROM educational_programs WHERE program_type = 'Workshop';
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE income > 50000;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 30 AND gender = 'Male' ORDER BY income DESC;
SELECT program_name, program_type, program_duration FROM educational_programs WHERE target_population = 'Students' ORDER BY program_duration ASC;
SELECT id, age, ethnicity, income FROM demographic_data WHERE gender = 'Female' AND (age BETWEEN 20 AND 40) ORDER BY age;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE income > 50000 AND ethnicity LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY age DESC, income ASC;
SELECT program_name, program_type FROM educational_programs WHERE program_type IN ('Online', 'In-person') ORDER BY program_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM demographics;
SELECT id, age, gender FROM demographics WHERE age > 30;
SELECT location, ethnicity FROM demographics WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT * FROM educational_background ORDER BY education_level ASC;
SELECT id, program_name, enrollment_date FROM program_enrollment WHERE enrollment_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM demographics;
SELECT age, gender, ethnicity FROM demographics WHERE gender='Male';
SELECT location, age FROM demographics WHERE age >= 30 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT demographics.id, education_level, specialized_training FROM demographics JOIN educational_background ON demographics.id = educational_background.demographic_id;
SELECT id, program_name FROM program_enrollment WHERE enrollment_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM demographic_data;
SELECT id, age, gender FROM demographic_data;
SELECT program_name, program_description FROM educational_programs;
SELECT population_name, population_size FROM marginalized_populations;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, program_id FROM program_participants;
SELECT * FROM program_participants WHERE participant_age > 25 ORDER BY participant_name ASC;

SELECT participant_name, program_name FROM program_participants INNER JOIN educational_programs ON program_participants.program_id = educational_programs.program_id WHERE educational_programs.program_duration > 12;
SELECT DISTINCT program_name FROM educational_programs WHERE program_duration BETWEEN 6 AND 12;

SELECT participant_name, participant_age, program_name FROM program_participants INNER JOIN educational_programs ON program_participants.program_id = educational_programs.program_id WHERE participant_age < 30 ORDER BY program_name DESC;
SELECT population_name, AVG(population_size) AS average_population_size FROM marginalized_populations GROUP BY population_name HAVING AVG(population_size) > 10000;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data;
SELECT student_id, age, gender FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 25;
SELECT program_name, program_type FROM education_programs ORDER BY program_name DESC;
SELECT participation_id, enrollment_date FROM program_participants WHERE enrollment_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT program_id, success_rate FROM program_performance WHERE success_rate >= 0.8;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data ORDER BY age DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT student_id, age, ethnicity FROM demographic_data WHERE gender='Male';

SELECT d.student_id, d.age, e.program_name, p.success_rate FROM demographic_data d JOIN program_participants pp ON d.student_id = pp.student_id JOIN education_programs e ON pp.program_id = e.program_id JOIN program_performance p ON e.program_id = p.program_id WHERE d.age > 25 AND p.success_rate > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM program_evaluations WHERE evaluation_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-06-30';

SELECT e.program_type, COUNT(pp.student_id) AS total_participants FROM education_programs e LEFT JOIN program_participants pp ON e.program_id = pp.program_id GROUP BY e.program_type ORDER BY total_participants DESC;
